original: Jerndal, Ebbe, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 23/3/08 i Gbg av disp. Harald August J. o. Sigrid Mathidda Artelius. iG. 33 m. Ingräd Forsberg. Barn: Jens f. 34, Tord 36, Rigmor 42. — Stud:ex. v. Gbgs h. real 27, Cand. med. dent. i Leipzig 29, tysk tandl. där 31, sv. dito 32. Prakt, i Gbg o. Kungälv sed. 32.
translated: Jerndal, Ebbe, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 23/3/08 in Gothenburg, to parents Harald August J. and Sigrid Mathidda Artelius. Married to Ingräd Forsberg in 1933. Children: Jens b. 1934, Tord b. 1936, Rigmor b. 1942. Education: graduated from Gothenburg high school in 1927, graduated as a Doctor of Dental Medicine in Leipzig in 1929, practiced as a German dentist there in 1931, and as a Swedish dentist in 1932. Worked as a dentist in Gothenburg and Kungälv since 1932.
